Is it porcelain?     
A thing to be picked up?

![china-jug](/assets/SingleJug.png){:class="img-responsive"}


Is it an antique? An heirloom? A symbol of class?    
Some thing inherited?
<br><br>


Is it the Wedgwood pattern? A cultural appropriation?     

![wedgewood](/assets/wedgewood.png){:class="img-responsive"}

<br><br>
Is it a mesh?    
Scaled?

![mesh](/assets/jugs.png){:class="img-responsive"}


Is it a file?    
Selected? Stored?

![file](/assets/file.png){:class="img-responsive"}
<br><br>


Is it the way it fits a hand?     
Inches? Centimeters? Or perhaps pixels?

<br><br>

Is it RGB data? A texture?     
Flattened?

![map](/assets/Model.jpg){:class="img-responsive"}

<br><br>



Is it data? Vertices in some cartesian idea of space?    


Or could it be how it sits on a table, some table, an idea of a table?
